headline: Northrop Grumman (NOC) Surpasses Q2 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: Northrop Grumman (NOC) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +5.96% and +2.94%, respectively, for the quarter ended June 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
